Item 7.01.  Regulation FD Disclosure.
 
   
 On October 21, 2008, The Steak n Shake Company (the "Company") announced the publication of a letter from Sardar Biglari, Chairman of the Board. The letter may be accessed at the Companys web site, . A copy of the letter is attached hereto as Exhibit 99.1.
   
