PRIOR AGREEMENTS
.
9.              The provisions contained herein shall serve to supplement and amend the provisions of the Agreement.  To the extent that the terms of this Amendment conflict with the terms of the Agreement, the provisions of this Amendment shall control in all respects.
EFFECT OF AMENDMENT
.
