INDIANAPOLIS
, April 24, 2009 /PRNewswire-FirstCall/ -- The Steak n Shake Company (NYSE: SNS) today announced its results for its second fiscal quarter 2009, which ended April 8, 2009.
Fiscal
Second
Quarter 2009 Results
Net earnings for the second quarter of fiscal year 2009 were $2.3 million, or $0.08 per diluted share, contrasted to a net loss of ($2.8 million), or ($0.10) per diluted share in the second quarter of fiscal year 2008.  operated 21 fewer
