he Purchase Date Capital Balance within twenty (20) days after submission of the dispute to them.  The Accountants determination shall be set forth in writing and shall be conclusive and binding upon the parties hereto, absent manifest error.  Purchaser shall pay the fe es of the Accountants in connection therewith.
