(c)        any Lien in existence on the Closing Date and set forth on and any Lien granted as a replacement or substitute therefor; that any such replacement or substitute Lien (i) except as permitted by , does not secure an aggregate amount of Indebtedness or other obligations, if any, greater than that secured on the Closing Date ( the aggregate amount of any permanent repayments and prepayments thereof since the Closing Date but only to the extent that such repayments and prepayments by their terms cannot be reborrowed or redrawn and do not occur in connection with a refinancing of all or a portion of such Indebtedness) and (ii) does not encumber any property other than the property subject thereto on the Closing Date (any such Lien, an );
