(v)          The Financial Institution has not entered into any agreement with any other person or entity pursuant to which it has agreed to comply with any entitlement orders or instructions with respect to any Designated Account.  Until the termination of this Control Agreement, the Financial Institution will not, without the written approval of the Collateral Agent, enter into any agreement with any person or entity pursuant to which it agrees to comply with any orders or instructions of such person with respect to any Designated Account.
 
